CheckAgeAsConfounder

This is to check if age is a confouding factor for expression, methylation, and the relation

The counts tables were generated previously using HTseq.sh shell script and merge.command on Hera. It removes the outlier data point from the analysis, which was patient 29. This script requires a transcript counts table. There is also a sample mapping file called patient_sample_mapping.csv which links the diagnosis the the samples. This file was most recently processed on Mon Jun 30 21:09:17 2014.

This step gets the protein coding genes only.
